      <title>Learning Objectives</title>
      <para id="id3072597">With 100% accuracy during a: memory building activity, exercises, lab assignment, problems, or timed quiz/exam; the student is expected to:</para>
      <list id="id4879784" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>Define the terms on the definitions as listed in the modules associated with this chapter.</item>
        <item>Acquire a general understanding of the pointer data type, the address and indirection operators, the concept of dereferencing.</item>
        <item>Given pseudocode, write the C++ code for a program that uses reference variables.</item>
      </list>
